---
title: Smokey Chicken & Roast Veggie Couscous with Lemon Yoghurt
description: Smokey paprika, brown sugar and lemon combine to give chicken an irresistible flavour boost. Perched on a bed of tender roast veggies and fluffy couscous, and topped with zesty lemon yoghurt, this has something for everyone.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5efe92d5fe59bd67e12a2adb-bbcbc315.jpg
